-- CIMB, two others seek merger to create Malaysia's biggest bank -media
-- By Al-Zaquan Amer Hamzah
-- Wed Jul 09, 2014 09:07PM EDT
-- None



KUALA LUMPUR, July 10 (Reuters) - Malaysia's CIMB Group Holdings Bhd <CIMB.KL>, RHB Capital Bhd <RHBC.KL> and Malaysia Building Society Bhd <MBSS.KL> will seek regulatory approval for a merger, aiming to create the country's largest bank, a newspaper said on Thursday.

